After all, it's been many long years since our people have set foot within Gundabad!\n\n'I have been asked to study the two distinct types of drakelings in Kordh Gúrat to the south-west, a level below the middle tier. I'll need a few samples of each, but I haven't been able to get close to them myself. If you could help me procure these samples, it would be much appreciated!'
You have collected a few samples from each type of drakeling.\n\nHórskur is waiting for you in Aslíf on the upper tier to return with the samples.
Kordh Gúrat is located to the south-west of Aslíf, a level below the middle tier.\n\nHórskur has asked for samples from each type of drakeling there.

'[placeholder], hello! I decided it was time to move on from studying the wildlife in Elderslade. After all, it's been many long years since my people have set foot within Gundabad!\n\n'I have been asked to study the two distinct types of drakelings in Kordh Gúrat to the south-west, a level below the middle tier. I'll need a few samples of each, but I haven't been able to get close to them myself. If you could help me procure these samples, it would be much appreciated!'
Hórskur's next area of study involves drakelings, but he doesn't have the samples he needs.
'All of these samples look quite useable, and you've procured enough for me to study. Thank you for your hard work, friend!'
